
<h3>Components</h3>
<div class="row">
    <p class="descriptive col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-lg-8">
        There are several components which come with this plugin. They share common characteristics and code but 
        will be covered separately. They are listed here, click on the one you're interested in for more details.
    </p>        
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
        <ul>
           <li>{{#link-to 'text-input'}}<code>text-input</code>{{/link-to}} - text input control</li>
           <li>{{#link-to 'number-input'}}<code>number-input</code>{{/link-to}} - numeric input control</li>
        <li>{{#link-to 'password-input'}}<code>password-input</code>{{/link-to}} - text input control for passwords</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
        <ul>
            <li>{{#link-to 'phone-input'}}<code>phone-input</code>{{/link-to}} - text input specifically for phone numbers</li>
